data.description: Quiet Cul-de-sac Ranch home w/ 3 car garage. Calm, cool, comforting, clean and fresh, "3 bed up, 1bed down" nearly home on a prime south facing lot. REAL hardwood floors & big windows in wide open main living area. Kitchen features gorgeous dark wood cabinets, quartz countertops, SS appliances, island with large dining area. Primary suite boasts counter height hard surface double vanities, and walk-in closet. Covered paver patio looks out on fully fenced yard with fire pit, perfect for spending time with friends or playing with kids & pets. Luxurious lower level has expansive rec room with gas fireplace and custom built-ins, 4th bedroom/office/workout area + 3/4 bath, great for guests, PLUS an office room. Radon mitigation already installed. Just a few minutes from shopping and Offutt .AFB. Only a few years young but priced well under new construction and you can move in right away with confidence! VA 5.2% assumable loan.
